      "value": "<p>Your martial training has helped you develop a particular style of fighting. As a result, you learn one Fighting Style option of your choice from the Fighter class. If you already have a style, the one you choose must be different. Whenever you gain a level, you can replace this feat's fighting style with another one from the Fighter class that you do not have. <strong>You are required to forgo two of your feat bullets to select Combat Initiate.</strong></p><section class=\"secret\" id=\"secret-K11plVhBi2RARnkU\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>When you select this feat, open the Class and Subclass Features compendium and select from the Fighting Styles folder in the Shared Features folder.</p></section>",
